# Docker Services

```bash
docker compose up -d                              # base: DB migrate, reader, crawlers
docker compose --profile ai up -d                 # + Ollama, polish-worker
docker compose --profile gpu up -d                # + audio workers
docker compose --profile audio up -d              # + audio-enqueuer
```

## Key env (see `docker/env.example`)

- `STORY_DATABASE_URL=postgresql://betterbox:betterbox@host.docker.internal:54329/betterbox_story`
- `AUDIO_VIENEU_VOICE_PROFILE=preset_binh_an`
- `AUDIO_SEGMENT_VIENEU_VOICE_KEY=preset_binh_an`
- `CRAWLER_ONLY_INCOMPLETE=1`, `ALTERNATE_APPLY=0`

## Notes

- GPU audio/polish often run locally, not in Docker containers
- Disabled sources in default Docker: `hako`, `manhwatv`, `qidian`, `naver_series`
- Scale crawlers: `CRAWLER_REPLICAS=3 docker compose up -d`
